        <options>
            <option letter="a">It had no effect on military operations</option>
            <option letter="b">It killed more troops than combat</option>
            <option letter="c">It only affected civilian populations</option>
            <option letter="d">It improved military medicine</option>
        </options>
        <answer>b</answer>
        <explanation>The Spanish Flu severely impacted military operations, killing more American troops than combat deaths in WWI, affecting troop movements and military effectiveness on both sides.</explanation>
