    <question>
        <prompt>How did the Palmer Raids affect civil liberties?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">They protected immigrant rights</option>
            <option letter="b">They violated constitutional rights</option>
            <option letter="c">They expanded voting rights</option>
            <option letter="d">They had no legal impact</option>
        </options>
        <answer>b</answer>
        <explanation>The Palmer Raids during the Red Scare violated constitutional rights through mass arrests and deportations of suspected radicals without due process, setting dangerous precedents for civil liberties.</explanation>
    </question>

